pageContext.claim: “I saw a statistic where it's worse than Honduras, right now..”
pageContext.analysis: This is a flawed apples-to-oranges comparison. Baltimore is a city, and Trump is comparing Baltimore, an urban area, to a country with a mix of urban and rural areas. It would be more relevant compare the state of Maryland to these countries: The state had a homicide rate of 9 per 100,000 people, compared to Honduras (41).
